title: iPhone Data Recovery + patch - Crackingpatching

Description: 
iPhone Data Recovery 1.0.26 a program from the name of which is already clear if you have an iOS-based device and you accidentally or specially deleted some files there and then wished to return them, but it's too late and do not know how to do it, this development will allow perform this task. Can recover your messages, photos, videos, audio files, documents, notes, call log, contacts and other data. You can also recover lost data from iTunes or iCloud backup. There is a preview mode, that is, before you restore the files you will be able to make sure that this is exactly what you were looking for. 
I advise everyone who encountered such a problem to download iPhone Data Recovery from us on the project, the version comes with a patch (key), you just need to unzip the archive, install the program, then copy the patch from another ZIP of the archive, if you do not know how to use it, read inside instructions. The Russian version is missing, but there are not enough chips here, it's quite possible to understand it ourselves.
